CREATE.PUT.PROPERTY.BY.NAME.METHOD: **************************************
* create a method to set a property value given the property name in     *
* a variable                                                             *
**************************************************************************
    GOSUB START.CREATE.TIME

    SOURCE.START = ""
    TARGET.START = ""
    SOURCE.LINE.COUNT = 0

    TARGET.COMMON.START = ""
    SOURCE.COMMON.START = ""
    SOURCE.COMMON.COUNT = 0

    PARAMETER.LIST = ""
    PARAMETER.BYREF.LIST = ""
    PARAMETER.SPECIAL.LIST = ""
